function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
--	Hydra.ActorEnable(gizmo_Ritualfx)
--	Need to replace with an effectgroup
	
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(MERCHANT_SON_2, false, true)
	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateInActorGroup("QST_Step_DemonLedger_DemonBoss_BruteUnique_Spawner")
	
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(MERCHANT_SON_2)
	
	local DemonBoss = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Step_DemonLedger_DemonBoss_BruteUnique")
	for i, Orrostus_02 in ipairs(DemonBoss) do
		Hydra.ActorDisableAI(Orrostus_02)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(Orrostus_02, true)
		
		tParticipants = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
		for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tParticipants) do
			Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(BOSS_SUMMON_CONV, idPlayer, Orrostus_02)
		end
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(MERCHANT_SON_2, PanicAnimKey, true)

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	end
